snippet.title: Johnny Depp and Amber Heard Tied the Knot on His Private Island - TOI
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp and Amber Heard Tied the Knot on His Private Island 

Johnny Depp and Amber Heard tied the knot in a gorgeous ceremony on the actor's private island in the Bahamas on Sunday.
